  "title": "Structural Design Engineer (Highrise/Precast Project)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Take the lead in C&S/Technical design functions; be in-charge for all (C&S) civil/structural site-based design matters being tasked</li><li>Attending and being proactive in design coordination meeting with consultants / client</li><li>Ensure drawing registry is maintained and latest drawings / BIM models are available for all parties involved</li><li>Ensure transmittal forms / emails are issued for latest drawings / BIM models,</li><li>To study & review drawings / specifications in identifying discrepancies and issue queries to consultants accordingly</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree and above in Civil/Structural or relevant engineering discipline</li><li>At least 3-5 years of prior experience with a contractor or consultant environment, focusing on C&S Design function</li></ul><p>If the role resonates with you and your professional experience complements the responsibilities listed, send your resume to <strong>koh.dickson@bayesrecruitment.com</strong></p><p>Dickson KOH, EA Registration R1103367</p><p>bayesrecruitment.com</p>",
